{"tid":1317945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講示威者，勇武嘅就叫義士","createTime":"2019-07-15T00:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T07:27:30.000Z","uid":255563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e73050cc610f3d9c33c6dae80ab5a2dfcfd5653a","tid":1317945,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:12:25.000Z","msg":"衝嘅叫義士<br />\n唔衝嘅叫香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫黑警<br />\n叫黨衛軍/政府軍<br />\n<br />\n例子：琴晚有幾十個義士制服咗個落單嘅政府軍，在場好多香港人係樓上嗌香港加油～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n效果：將警察稱呼換成黨衛軍/政府軍，可以係輿論上減低佢哋鎮壓香港人嘅合法性。<br />\n<br />\n示威者稱呼 會令人覺得嗰啲只係社會嘅一部分人<br />\n轉用香港人吧，反正有二百萬人出過來，這種轉換，不為過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理據：佢哋冇number,冇委任證，而家仲要反光物料蒙面，根本已經係歷史書入面獨裁國家內戰嗰啲秘密警察同軍閥系統咁<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，香港人會習慣同明明，自己面對緊嘅係軍閥政府"},{"pid":"c07a2cb849feabe7b6d945b7cf19d73ecd87c831","tid":1317945,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8gzTfp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8gzTfp.png&h=72d78667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsawVtL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsawVtL.png&h=5be42adc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqXn2iZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqXn2iZ.png&h=6b8d4efa&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f218a0a68c94810e4c4b3f781dc1cd0f8ac440fc","tid":1317945,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RVHZs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RVHZs9.png&h=cdb97609&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62b674c87aa69586fbb3d77e524b73562619a543","tid":1317945,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a616367cf35a6cbe3bf2a654f20924f92be2cb6a","tid":1317945,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited